carefully plan the projects to be included under the Local Government Development Program Priority Projects for Funding which embodies the projects to be specifically funded by the 20% Development Fund and see to it that the items partake the nature of capital expenditures;
instruct the BAC and the Municipal Accountant to submit the absent documents to support the disbursement of municipal funds;
